{"word":"G2252 - ἤμην - ḗmēn - ay'-mane - Be","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἤμην</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ḗmēn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ay'-mane</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரு (நிச்சயமாக இருத்தல்) - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"assuredly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G2358 - θριαμβεύω - thriambeúō - three-am-byoo'-o/2358\">G2358</a>; I <i>was</i>. (Sometimes unexpressed.): - be, was. [Sometimes unexpressed.]</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}